{"word":"G1981 - ἐπισκηνόω - episkēnóō - ep-ee-skay-no'-o - Rest upon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισκηνόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">episkēnóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-skay-no'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Rest upon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தங்கு"},{"paragraph":"to fix a tent or habitation on"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4637 - σκηνόω - skēnóō - skay-no'-o/4637\">G4637</a>; to <i>tent upon</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>abide with:</i> - rest upon.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1981/1981\">G1981</a>, <a href=\"#/G2681/2681\">G2681</a>, <a href=\"#/G4633/4633\">G4633</a>, <a href=\"#/G4634/4634\">G4634</a>, <a href=\"#/G4635/4635\">G4635</a>, <a href=\"#/G4636/4636\">G4636</a>, <a href=\"#/G4637/4637\">G4637</a>, <a href=\"#/G4638/4638\">G4638</a>"}]}